name: Greenteeth
description:
Trying to make a game for the jam in a sleep deprived state was not a good idea. This is not a complete game. It isn't really a game in the current state that it is in. With the time I spent working on this I was able to form an idea and make a conceptual level. There is not a way to quit the game just yet so you have to force quit. 
Apologies for the "game" but I wanted to submit a concept at the very least to the jam. 

I missed the deadline trying to make the page :/
